   <tr height="180" style='height:108.00pt;'>
    <td class="xl66" height="180" align="right" style='height:108.00pt;' x:num>45652</td>
    <td class="xl66" x:str>API Endpoints &quot;Get settings - update settings&quot;</td>
    <td class="xl66" x:str>Get Settings GET /admin/settings Return grouped settings.Only accessible by Admin role. 🔹 Update Settings (Per Section) PUT /admin/settings/{group} Validate payload.Update multiple keys inside that group.Return updated data. 🔹 Toggle Setting Status PATCH /admin/settings/{key}/toggle Switch is_active state.Return updated status.</td>
