    <td class="xl66" x:str>General Settings Tab</td>
    <td class="xl66" x:str>Phone Number * Field Type: Text input Validation: RequiredMust be valid phone number formatRegex example: ^&amp;#91;0-9+\-\s&amp;#93;{7,15}$ Max length: 20 charactersTrim whitespaceStore in international format (recommended) Errors: &quot;Phone number is required.&quot;&quot;Invalid phone number format.&quot; 2️⃣ E-mail * Field Type: Email input Validation: RequiredMust be valid email formatMax length: 255 charactersMust follow standard RFC email format Errors: &quot;Email is required.&quot;&quot;Invalid email address.&quot; 3️⃣ Facebook Field Type: URL input Validation: OptionalMust be valid URL format (if provided)Must start with: https:// Max length: 255Optional: Must contain facebook.com Errors: &quot;Invalid Facebook URL.&quot; 4️⃣ Twitter Field Type: URL input Validation: OptionalMust be valid URL (if provided)Must start with: https:// Max length: 255Optional: Must contain twitter.com or x.com Errors: &quot;Invalid Twitter URL.&quot; 5️⃣ LinkedIn Field Type: URL input Validation: OptionalValid URL formatMust start with: https:// Optional: Must contain linkedin.comMax length: 255 Errors: &quot;Invalid LinkedIn URL.&quot; 6️⃣ Instagram Field Type: URL input Validation: OptionalValid URL formatMust start with: https:// Optional: Must contain instagram.comMax length: 255 Errors: &quot;Invalid Instagram URL.&quot; 🖼 Logo Upload Fields 7️⃣ Original Logo (Recommended size: 180x60) Field Type: File upload (image) Validation: Optional (or Required based on business rule)Allowed types: jpgjpegpngsvg (optional) Max file size: 2MB Recommended dimensions: 180x60 px Validate image mime typeStore in public storage Errors: &quot;Invalid file type.&quot;&quot;File size exceeds 2MB.&quot;&quot;Logo should be 180x60 px.&quot; 8️⃣ White Logo (Recommended size: 180x60) Field Type: File upload (image) Validation: Same rules as Original LogoDimensions: 180x60 px 9️⃣ Small Logo (Recommended size: 50x50) Field Type: File upload (image) Validation: Image onlyMax 2MBRecommended dimensions: 50x50 px Square image preferred Errors: &quot;Small logo must be 50x50 px.&quot;</td>
