   <tr height="682.50" style='height:409.50pt;'>
    <td class="xl66" height="682.50" align="right" style='height:409.50pt;' x:num>45774</td>
    <td class="xl66" x:str>[Admin-3] user story Admin Manage Academic Structures Master Data</td>
    <td class="xl66" x:str>Title: Admin can manage Academic Year, Subject, Curriculum Track, and Accrediting Bodies As a System Administrator I want to Add, edit, and activate/deactivate Academic Years, Subjects, Curriculum Tracks, and Accrediting Bodies So that I can manage the academic master data dynamically from the admin panel without developer intervention. 📌 Acceptance Criteria 1️⃣ Common Requirements for All Modules Applies to: Academic Year (السنه الدراسيه)Subject (المواد)Curriculum Track (المسار التعليمى)Accrediting Bodies (جهات الاعتماد) Add Admin can create a new record.Admin must enter: Name (Arabic) – requiredName (English) – required System validates required fields.System saves record with Active = true by default. Edit Admin can edit: Name (Arabic)Name (English) Changes are saved successfully.Validation rules apply on edit. Toggle Status Admin can toggle status between: ActiveInactive Status change is reflected immediately in listing.Inactive records should not appear in public-facing or dependent dropdowns. Listing Admin can view paginated list.Admin can see: Name (Arabic)Name (English)Status (Active / Inactive)Actions (Edit / Toggle) Search &amp; Filter Admin can search by: Arabic nameEnglish name Admin can filter by: ActiveInactive</td>
    <td class="xl68" align="right" x:num="46329.000069444446">03/11/2026 00:00</td>
    <td class="xl68" align="right" x:num="46329.">03/11/2026 00:00</td>
    <td class="xl66" x:str>Ahmed Abdelfattah</td>
