    <td class="xl66" x:str>[Warehouse] Update the API for new fields</td>
    <td class="xl66" x:str>Create API for listing, adding, editing, deleting and get by ID for the warehouse address 1 - National Address 2- Name of the Branch 3- Active flag in database &quot;Active - deactive&quot;</td>
