   <tr height="320" style='height:192.00pt;'>
    <td class="xl66" height="320" align="right" style='height:192.00pt;' x:num>46356</td>
    <td class="xl66" x:str>[Bank Accpount ]Update When Status is Pending or rejcted</td>
    <td class="xl66" x:str>If bank account status is: pending User is allowed to update the bank account. Example cases: Correct IBANChange bankUpdate Swift codeReplace proof document Rule 2 – Update When Status is Rejected If bank account status is: rejected User is allowed to update the bank account. Purpose: Fix incorrect information.Upload corrected proof document. Rule 3 – Update Not Allowed When Approved If bank account status is: approved User cannot update the bank account. Response example: Bank account cannot be updated after approval. If user wants changes: User must create a new bank account.</td>
