    <td class="xl66" x:str>Mobile and Email fields are cleared after updating data from backend</td>
    <td class="xl66" x:str>Description: After making any update to the Mobile or Email fields and saving the changes, the data in these fields is unexpectedly deleted in the backend. As a result, the fields appear empty after the update, even though valid data was entered and saved. The system should retain the updated values instead of removing them. Actual Result: The Mobile and Email values are deleted or saved as empty in the backend after the update. Expected Result: The Mobile and Email fields should retain and save the updated values correctly in the backend.</td>
