    <td class="xl66" x:str>Refresh button in chat screen shows &quot;Coming Soon&quot; and &quot;Unauthorized&quot;</td>
    <td class="xl66" x:str>Description: When the user clicks the refresh button while on the chat screen, unexpected messages appear including &quot;Coming Soon&quot; and &quot;This page will be here soon&quot;. The refresh action should update the chat messages instead of displaying these messages. Expected Result: The chat screen should refresh and display the latest messages. Actual Result: A message saying &quot;Coming Soon&quot; appears and &quot;This page will be here soon&quot; is displayed instead of refreshing the chat.</td>
