   <tr height="180" style='height:108.00pt;'>
    <td class="xl66" height="180" align="right" style='height:108.00pt;' x:num>46598</td>
    <td class="xl66" x:str>System allows setting start time before end time incorrectly when creating a warehouse</td>
    <td class="xl66" x:str>Description: When creating a warehouse, the system allows entering an invalid delivery time range where the start time is after the end time. Expected Result: The system should validate the delivery time and prevent saving if the start time is later than the end time. A validation message should appear to notify the user.</td>
