    <td class="xl66" x:str>Description: When editing the profile data, the changes should not affect the School Info section. However, when the user updates the email address in the profile, the email is also updated in School Info, which is not the expected behavior. Expected Result: Updating the profile email should only affect the profile data and should not change any data in School Info. Actual Result: The email change in profile is also reflected in School Info, which should not happen.</td>
