    <td class="xl66" x:str>Description: There is an inconsistency in the validation of the Capacity field under Production Capacity &amp; Shipping. The field is marked as required when adding a new product, but it is not required when editing an existing product, which causes inconsistent behavior in the form validation. Expected Result: The Capacity field validation should be consistent in both Add Product and Edit Product (either required in both or optional in both). Actual Result: The Capacity field is required in Add Product but not required in Edit Product.</td>
