    <td class="xl66" x:str>Add Product button disabled when Trade Term is FOB and RFQ is selected</td>
    <td class="xl66" x:str>Description: When adding a product, if the Trade Term is set to FOB and the user selects RFQ, the Add Product button becomes disabled. This prevents the user from submitting the product, even though all required fields are filled correctly. Expected Result: The Add Product button should remain enabled and allow the product to be submitted. Actual Result: The Add Product button is disabled, preventing the product submission.</td>
